      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Fair-condition car that is usable and presentable, but clearly not a mint or fully sorted example. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear such as paint imperfections, interior wear, and other age-related blemishes, and it may need some maintenance or repairs depending on how picky you are. That said, it should still be a reasonable option for someone looking for a more affordable driver project or budget-friendly vehicle rather than a showpiece.",
